{
  "text": "The tacnode RHP which is mentioned in Sections 1.4.1 and 1.4.2 was defined in [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , and [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] require only asymptotics in sectors ∆ j , so there is some freedom to choose the jump matrices corresponding to different solutions to (1.18a). The relation between the RHP 1.5 and the tacnode RHP is as follows.",
